How to use under WebAppStore Project

first from all read this page http://ibotpeaches.github.io/Apktool/install/

make this file executable chmod 755
-------------------------------------
chmod 755 apktool
chmod 755 apktool.jar


copy two files apktool and apktool.jar to /usr/bin
---------------------------------------------------
sudo cp apktool /usr/bin
sudo cp apktool.jar /usr/bin